---
/**
 * CoverageCard — "Your Belongings Are Covered" card
 * showing £15k per van Goods in Transit liability details.
 */
---

<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
  <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-primary-200 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-green-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-lg uppercase tracking-wide">Included</div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Your Belongings Are Covered</h2>
    <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">£15,000 <span class="text-lg font-normal text-warm-gray">per van</span></div>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-warm-gray mb-6">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Goods in Transit liability included on every move as standard</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Aggregate cover per Luton van (not per item)</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Repair or replacement — whichever costs less</li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">!</span> Items over £2,000 must be declared in writing before the move</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium">No admin fee. No opt-in. You're covered from day one.</p>
  </div>
</div>
